  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7 ? \u0b9c\u0bc7.\u0bb5\u0bbf.\u0baa\u0bbf.\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Where are the rifles? President Ranil asked the leader of JVP",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Observing the changes and events in Sri Lanka's national politics is always a cause for concern.",
        "It is the first time in Sri Lanka's and world's political history that a person has been elected president with just 134 votes.",
        "However, Ranil Wickramasinghe has realized his long-held dream of the throne. Elections did not help him to achieve this goal of political success. Instead, it was the 'sanctuary' struggle that led.",
        "As the situation is like this, as the voting for the election of the President was held on Wednesday, Anukumara Dissanayake of the People's Liberation Front (JVP) has come against him by entering the Parliament that day.",
        "\"Where are the two guns?\" asked President Ranil. Anura replied that which guns with a small chainsaw.",
        "Anura said that President Ranil said that he would ask for those guns if you went to Kalawadi from the army during the parliamentary demonstration, but don't joke and ask the people who took them away. President Ranil left there saying that it is okay to hand over to the army as soon as possible.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe took the oath of office the next day Thursday on the 2nd floor of Parliament where the offices of the President and Prime Minister are located.",
        "Many party leaders were also present in this event. The President mentioned to the party leaders who congratulated President Ranil Wickremesinghe after his swearing-in that he would take steps to establish an all-party government as soon as possible.",
        "During this, Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa said, I will not call you 'Athimedaku'. President Ranil said to Wickremesinghe that you have mentioned not to call like that.",
        "The President replied, \"I have banned the word 'Athimethaku'.\" So he said with a smile that if you use that word, you will be punished. The bystanders, including the Leader of the Opposition, had a silent smile.",
        "In both these incidents, the political repercussions of President Ranil Wickremesinghe can be felt.",
        "President Ranil is the one who can fully use the executive power given in the constitution.",
        "After Gotabaya Rajapaksa took office, he abolished the 19th constitution and regained executive power, but the media could not benefit from that power.",
        "On the other hand, Ranil Wickramasinghe handed over the complete executive power he had acquired and fled the country.",
        "Today, Ranil Wickremesinghe is in office as the Executive President. Play the Game But Follow the Rules (Play the Game But Follow the Rules) Former President J.R. This text is Jayawardena's political teaching.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe has come to power after years of waiting. Although nothing is possible before the Lok Sabha, the political games of President Ranil Wickremesinghe who followed the rule for a short period of time can be seen."
      ],
